As a consequence of this work, JPL is investing resources to research and development for this sampler so that it can one day earn the right to be sponsored by NASA for a comet samplering mission. For a detailed summary of my work, you can visit JPL's publication titled /Sampling System Concepts for a Touch-and-Go Architecture Comet Surface Sample Return Mission/ [files/cssr.pdf here]. 
